description: Bentos Lunch starts with whole foods and made-from-scratch recipes to ensure the freshest quality. Using eco-friendly packaging, Bentos is a crisp alternative you can have delivered to your door or office! We also offer the same quality and attention to detail in our food cart services. We are an American twist on a Japanese tradition. Because Bentos concentrates on using only whole foods, you can count on a flavorful and healthy meal prepared just for your event! We offer a wide selection of options and can cater to your specific needs.
name: Bentos Lunch
